            <h2 class="text-center">Joining the Unit</h2>

            <p>In real life, 1st and 2nd Commando Regiment operators are hand picked specialists. Here at SOCOMD, we
                strive to achieve the realism and immersion aspects of MILSIM in Arma 3, while mimicking the operational
                aspects of 1st and 2nd Commando Regiments, as well as their supporting elements.
                Therefore we need all members to be mature minded in order to join SOCOMD. A selection process is in
                place to ensure the quality of potential operators, that is the questionnaires in this initial
                application form and a formal interview afterwards, if successful.</p>

            <p><b>All applicants need to be at least 18 years of age to apply.</b> They also need to obtain the correct
                mindset to join our MILSIM group and be able to participate various training, operations and essentially
                role play as a special forces soldier in game using realistic tactics and procedures.
                We do appreciate any underage applicants’ genuine interest and their pursuit of MILSIM, and we look
                forward to their application once they reach our minimum age limit of 18 years old.
                Note: It is advised that all applicants are being honest and serious with their application’s
                information.</p>

            <p class="text-center"><b>Any deliberate misleading information in the application form will ultimately lead
                    to a
                    dishonourable discharge from SOCOMD and a possible ban of the applicant/member.</b></p>

